version_description: Same as some other versions I saw, but this one has all the lyrics written out. Also no distracting piano chords beside the guitar chords.
Slightly easier version to play. Capo on 4th fret. It works pretty well playing along to the acoustic version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TtSKnmmEkhw.

song_name: Baby Im A Big Star Now
